# Replaces einsum and 5D reshape ops with QNN-compatible alternatives, rewrites convex_upsample for export,
# and replaces the custom bilinear_grid_sample with F.grid_sample (bilinear) which QNN maps natively
# to its own grid sampler op — single call, no int64 indices, compatible with QNN HTP and TFLite.
#
